title: STRAP configuration for 820-4924
message: I wanted to upgrade an 820-4924 to 16GB Micron RAM DDR3. Is there a strap configuration for Micron branded memory?

title: STRAP configuration for 820-4924
message:
On the page 2 (BOM Configuration) I only see Hynix, Elpida and Samsung chips supported.
If you want to try, must play with the 4 RAMCFG lines.
